title: Tiled Watchface Premium Unlock Key
summary: Unlock the premium features in Tiled Watchface!
description: Install this to unlock the following features in Tiled Watchface:- Month overview.- Freely resizable tiles.- Unlimited number of pre-configured sets of tiles.
descriptionHTML:
Install this to unlock the following features in Tiled Watchface:
- Month overview.
- Freely resizable tiles.
- Unlimited number of pre-configured sets of tiles.
